      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "1. Digitization of curriculum (1 unit) which will be accessed by Facilitators for the weekly and monthly sessions.2. Six trainings for the facilitators to enhance their understanding of gender norms and behaviors, and community level diffusion.3. Weekly and Monthly sessions conducted for a duration of 21 months in total attended by the 400 individuals (200 couples)4. Community level activities organized by the groups targeted at community level diffusion.6. Media mobilization including radio program broadcasting for at least 39 weeks, social media campaign, posters and IVR system."
